<%- include('partials/header') %>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);
    padding: 70px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  [data-theme="dark"] .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #0F172A 100%); }
  .page-hero-icon {
    width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(0,229,160,0.15);
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 18px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: #FFFFFF; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .page-content { padding: 56px 0; background: var(--bg-body); }
  .content-wrapper { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  
  .policy-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: clamp(20px, 4vw, 32px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .policy-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .policy-card h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.3rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .policy-card h2 i { color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .policy-card p { color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .policy-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .policy-card ul li {
    padding: 8px 0; color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
  }
  .policy-card ul li i { color: var(--success); margin-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  
  .timeline-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .step-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 14px;
    background: var(--bg-card-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .step-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .step-num {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary-gradient);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .step-label { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .step-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4; }
  
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 48px 0; }
    .page-hero-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .page-content { padding: 36px 0; }
    .policy-card { padding: 20px; }
    .timeline-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
    .policy-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .policy-card ul li { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  }
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-icon"><i class="fas fa-undo-alt"></i></div>
  <h1 class="page-hero-title">Returns & Exchanges</h1>
</div>

<div class="page-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Our Return Policy</h2>
        <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy with your order, we offer a <strong>7-day return policy</strong> from the date of delivery. Items must be unused, in original packaging, and in the same condition as received.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-list-ol"></i> How to Return an Item</h2>
        <div class="timeline-steps">
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-label">Contact Us</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Email us at shopnest.management@gmail.com with your order number and reason for return</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-label">Get Approval</div>
            <div class="step-desc">We'll review your request and send return instructions within 24-48 hours</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-label">Return Package</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Pack the item securely and ship it to our return address in Sri Lanka</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Eligible Items</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Items must be unused and in original condition</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Original packaging must be intact</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Return request must be made within 7 days of delivery</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Proof of purchase is required</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Non-Returnable Items</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-times"></i> Items marked as final sale</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-times"></i> Gift cards</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-times"></i> Personal care items (for hygiene reasons)</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-times"></i> Items damaged by customer misuse</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-undo"></i> Refunds</h2>
        <p>Once we receive and inspect your return, we will notify you via email. If approved, your refund will be processed to your original payment method within <strong>5-10 business days</strong>. Delivery charges are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.</p>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>